Covers the contractual costs for storing, packaging, addressing brochures, and other printed matter. Also, distribution and mailing costs paid via the Purchase Card Program. Excludes postage costs covered under Object Class Code 2341.. Covers the cost of supply items not otherwise classified. Includes petty cash purchases as distinguished from specific purpose vouchers..
